0:15:57.661,000 --> 0:15:59,000
We need eight hours of sleep a night.

332
0:16:01.392,000 --> 0:16:02,000
That's an average.

333
0:16:02.572,000 --> 0:16:04,000
Some people need more. Some people need less.

